# Code owners — Coffeetaria (desofs2026_wed_ffs_3)
#
# GitHub automatically requests a review from the listed owners on every PR
# whose base branch carries this file (main and develop). The PR author is
# never requested, so on any given PR the remaining owners are asked to review.
#
# Owners must have write access to the repository (all three do).
#
# To make a code-owner approval *mandatory* (not just requested), enable
# "Require review from Code Owners" in the branch protection rules for
# main / develop. Leaving it off keeps the auto-request without hard-blocking
# the team — recommended while close to a deadline.

# Default: every file requires a review from one of the main reviewers.
